casebody.data:
L.T. TUCKER, Jr., Petitioner
v.
CORIZON CORRECTIONAL HEALTH CARE, et al. No. 19-5342 Supreme Court of the United States. October 7, 2019

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition *337for a writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
